{"tid":374073,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"個女仔是咪有暗示？","createTime":"2017-08-25T13:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T03:50:30.000Z","uid":88343,"like":7,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f14e4d2ac581cfbc4ec711621749f7d5c979ce1","tid":374073,"uid":88343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"咁話說呢我前日生日，原本plan咗去海馬公園，但因為打風冇得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好采海馬公園都有豁免，前日生日嘅人可以係一個月內去返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好喇入正題，咁尋日去到其中一個園區玩果陣經過一堆攤位遊戲，可能時間仲早就冇乜人玩（其實我覺得係唔底玩啲人先唔玩）。咁有一檔係一個後生女睇檔，佢個樣呢就睇落幾清純，似現役女大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攤位個女仔=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一經過佢就係咁話'玩啦玩啦'咁，我過埋嗰檔佢仲講緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，搞到我忍唔住拎轉頭同佢搖手笑住咁示意不了，同埋順便再𥄫吓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知佢仲繼續望住我講'玩啦玩啦'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我就係度諗：唔通佢講嘅野別有用心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係度想問吓大家覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =去馬啦，人地做到咁出面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =收皮啦你，諗多咗喇"},{"pid":"58786d2cf50cfe325bd98aa022bc4bf4306de096","tid":374073,"uid":20448,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:12:59.000Z","msg":"樓下保安啊姐同你講早晨<br />\n你會唔會覺得佢想同你做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6c1aebb0194ba997a5c50cf7b59a78e329905d","tid":374073,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:13:07.000Z","msg":"好明顯想同你做愛"},{"pid":"77a742aab52c002